  "texts": [
    "In this context, a feedback system that offers tailored guidance to facilitate student progression is essential.",
    "Students are more likely to respond to and benefit from feedback when there is a sense of connection with the feedback provider, i.e. their educators.",
    "The findings of this study indicate a recognition among educators of the potential of and challenges in the use of AI tools in expediting the feedback provision process and enhancing the quality of feedback provided.",
    "Integrating AI tools requires maintaining a balance between the efficiency of feedback mechanisms and their personalisation to support students' learning and development.",
    "In the absence in the literature of a critical assessment of AI-provided feedback, a significant area for future research also emerges."
  ],
